{"tid":1085710,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"揀興趣定錢途","createTime":"2019-03-31T10:57:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-02T07:04:03.000Z","uid":201336,"like":4,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"f20189274b4e9e9f05be0c37a1f75a057bb5ad79","tid":1085710,"uid":201336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T10:57:26.000Z","msg":"讀緊大學year1諗住quit u reju<br />\n一個option係讀醫護，第時工作穩定高月入<br />\n另一個option係讀media，自己有興趣而且讀落冇咁大壓力<br />\n已經苦惱左好耐，我知有時錢都可以為我帶嚟快樂，平時有閒錢去旅行食好嘢都會好開心<br />\n但另一邊係我夢想嘅lifestyle，做啲唔悶唔重覆嘅嘢，有機會接觸全世界，寓工作於娛樂。<br />\n有人話讀專科先有保障，又有人話只要有興趣就做乜都可以成功。<br />\n唔該揾人點醒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 夠分"},{"pid":"dbadeb9ff17d996edc248f9b647910250883606d","tid":1085710,"uid":188297,"like":4,"dislike":12,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T10:58:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d10e425888004b13f623db954b7b7e8c3d0d179e","tid":1085710,"uid":203517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T10:58:30.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"55d0542065ffb627ef13faaff935f8b7ac67fe5b","tid":1085710,"uid":83904,"like":33,"dislike":2,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T10:58:56.000Z","msg":"興趣<br />\n無興趣既工你都做得唔耐同唔會舒服"},{"pid":"be7e1e2e5cae4e20eea9e6f180c06f480b886b27","tid":1085710,"uid":44534,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T11:00:57.000Z","msg":"錢 有錢解決好多野 生活好多問題都處理到"},{"pid":"7d4ea1fc8deb0c3c84874632608c0ef7f89a3197","tid":1085710,"uid":71237,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T11:01:50.000Z","msg":"你又知自己對media有興趣?<br />\n試過拍片未?"},{"pid":"b234bf2e2f7218f1123a0b3aca36dc09b42bd2dc","tid":1085710,"uid":7376,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T11:02:32.000Z","msg":"搵到錢 閑時咪玩下自己興趣"},{"pid":"9edb163167cf7edd97520b25b8ded72f7b1b43ac","tid":1085710,"uid":29929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T11:05:45.000Z","msg":"有條件簡興趣既人係有錢/成績超然既人<br />\n<br />\